"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Donald Trump won the Republican primary in South Carolina, beating Nikki Haley. Haley, the former governor of the state, could not convince voters that she would be a better candidate for the general election.\",            \"english_title\": \"Donald Trump's victory in South Carolina's Republican primary\",            \"translated_version\": \"Donald Trump gan\u00f3 la primaria republicana en Carolina del Sur, venciendo a Nikki Haley. Haley, la ex gobernadora del estado, no pudo convencer a los votantes de que ser\u00eda una mejor candidata para la elecci\u00f3n general.\",            \"translated_title\": \"La victoria de Donald Trump en la primaria republicana de Carolina del Sur\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The body of Alexei Navalny, the Russian opposition leader who died in prison, was returned to his mother. His press secretary mentioned that the funeral arrangements are pending, and there are concerns about potential interference by authorities.\",            \"english_title\": \"Return of Alexei Navalny's body to his mother\",            \"translated_version\": \"El cuerpo de Alexei Navalny, el l\u00edder de la oposici\u00f3n rusa que muri\u00f3 en prisi\u00f3n, fue devuelto a su madre. Su secretario de prensa mencion\u00f3 que los arreglos funerarios est\u00e1n pendientes y hay preocupaciones sobre posibles interferencias de las autoridades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Devoluci\u00f3n del cuerpo de Alexei Navalny a su madre\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"ECOWAS, a group of West African states, removed sanctions imposed on Niger following a military coup. The decision was made due to humanitarian reasons and to discourage the junta and neighboring countries from leaving the bloc.\",            \"english_title\": \"ECOWAS lifting sanctions on Niger\",            \"translated_version\": \"ECOWAS, un grupo de estados de \u00c1frica Occidental, levant\u00f3 las sanciones impuestas a N\u00edger tras un golpe militar. La decisi\u00f3n se tom\u00f3 por razones humanitarias y para desalentar a la junta y a los pa\u00edses vecinos de abandonar el bloque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"ECOWAS levanta sanciones a N\u00edger\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Warren Buffett, the head of Berkshire Hathaway, cautioned about the declining performance of the firm. He highlighted the lack of lucrative investment opportunities and the record-high cash reserves of $167.6bn.\",            \"english_title\": \"Warren Buffett's warning on Berkshire Hathaway's performance\",            \"translated_version\": \"Warren Buffett, el jefe de Berkshire Hathaway, advirti\u00f3 sobre el declive en el rendimiento de la empresa. Destac\u00f3 la falta de oportunidades de inversi\u00f3n lucrativas y las reservas de efectivo r\u00e9cord de $167.6bn.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de Warren Buffett sobre el rendimiento de Berkshire Hathaway\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Western leaders, including Ursula von der Leyen and other prime ministers, visited Kyiv to express solidarity with Ukraine on the anniversary of Russia's invasion. They pledged financial, economic, military, and moral support to Ukraine.\",            \"english_title\": \"European leaders showing solidarity with Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"L\u00edderes occidentales, incluyendo a Ursula von der Leyen y otros primeros ministros, visitaron Kyiv para expresar solidaridad con Ucrania en el aniversario de la invasi\u00f3n de Rusia. Prometieron apoyo financiero, econ\u00f3mico, militar y moral a Ucrania.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edderes europeos mostrando solidaridad con Ucrania\"        }    ]}"